🎯 10 Most Asked Computer Network Interview Questions (PRODUCT LEVEL)
1️⃣ Why is TCP reliable?

Uses ACK, sequencing, retransmission.

2️⃣ Why do we use UDP?

For speed and real-time communication.

3️⃣ What causes congestion?

Traffic exceeding network capacity.

4️⃣ What is end-to-end principle?

Logic handled at endpoints, not network.

5️⃣ What is packet loss?

Loss of packets due to congestion/errors.

6️⃣ What is jitter?

Variation in delay.

7️⃣ What is throughput?

Actual data transferred.

8️⃣ What is latency?

Time delay.

9️⃣ What is buffering?

Temporary data storage to handle delays.

🔟 What is QoS?

Ensuring performance for critical traffic.

